  "title": "SRE Teaching \u2014 Golden Signals (RED)",
  "uid": "sre-golden-signals",
  "version": 1,
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## RED Method (Google SRE)\n\nFor **user-facing services**, monitor three signals:\n\n- **Rate** \u2014 How much demand? (requests/sec, transactions/sec)\n- **Errors** \u2014 What fraction fail? (5xx ratio, failed business operations)\n- **Duration** \u2014 How long do requests take? (p50/p95/p99 latency)\n\n**Why not CPU/memory?** Resource metrics tell you about *machines*, not *users*. A service can be slow while CPU looks fine (DB lock, downstream timeout).\n\n**Exercise:** Pick a service in the dropdown. If error rate spikes but rate is flat \u2192 quality problem. If rate drops and errors spike \u2192 overload or dependency failure.\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Rate \u2014 requests/sec",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "decimals": 2
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "colorMode": "value"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(ecommerce:http_request_rate:5m{service=~\"$service\"})",
          "legendFormat": "Rate \u2014 requests/sec",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Errors \u2014 5xx ratio",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 6,
        "y": 5
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "decimals": 2,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 0.01
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 0.05
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "colorMode": "value"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "avg(ecommerce:http_error_rate:5m{service=~\"$service\"})",
          "legendFormat": "Errors \u2014 5xx ratio",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
