      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Percentiles matter:** p95/p99 reveal tail latency that averages hide. SLOs are often written on p99 (e.g. 99% of requests < 500ms).\n\n**Recording rules:** `ecommerce:http_*` metrics are pre-computed in PrometheusRule `ecommerce-app-rules` \u2014 faster dashboards, consistent alert thresholds.\n"
